## User bar (VX) widget

![](data:image/png;base64,)

The **User bar (VX)** widget includes various Voxel components suitable to display in the header of your site.

Components available:

- **Notifications:** Displays notifications relevant to the current user
- **Messages:** Displays direct messages that user has received
- **User menu:** Displays user avatar and username and can toggle a menu
- **Menu:** Can be used to toggle any menu
- **Custom link:** Allows you to display a custom link component e.g link to Login, Register etc.

For each component, you can set

- Icon
- Label
- Control label responsive visibility
- Control component responsive visibility

If you need to make a specific component only visible for logged in user, you can apply [visibility rules](docs.getvoxel.io_article_visibility-rules-condition-and-restrict-content_.md) to it.
